item.title: How do i get my ready-made rsps online?
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

  1. Port forward your router for port 43594 and your computers IPv4 address (it’s the 192.168.XXX.XXX in your network and sharing center)
  2. Verify it’s port forwarded.
  3. Change the IP in the client to the one found here.
  4. Turn the server on
  5. Send the client out to a close friend and see if they can connect. If yes, then you’re all set, if no. you need to troubleshoot why.

Troubleshooting includes going to http://canyouseeme.org to see if your port is open. Double checking that your IP’s in the client are correct. And making sure the server/client have no errors when players attempt to connect.
